Package: EasyTidy
Title: Simplify Data Tidying and Transformation with EasyTidy
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jacky", "Yiu", , "jackyyiu0810@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-4273-0051"))
Description: EasyTidy is a user-friendly R package designed to streamline data tidying and transformation processes. It provides a collection of functions to simplify common tasks related to data cleaning, reshaping, and manipulation. EasyTidy leverages popular packages like dplyr and tidy to offer an intuitive and efficient way to prepare and transform datasets, reducing the complexity often associated with these operations. It aims to simplify and accelerate the data preparation phase, making it accessible to both beginners and experienced R users.
